</p>
<p>Let's try it guys: go back and refresh.</p>
<p>Click "Change to New Zealander". Ok, <code>$99.93</code> - that <em>looks</em> about right. Remember,
the upgrade should cost about $100, but since we've been using the old plan for
a few minutes, the true cost should be <em>slightly</em> lower.</p>
<h2 id="finishing-up-the-js">Finishing up the JS <a class="headerlink" href="upgrade-upcoming-invoice-process#finishing-up-the-js" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Ok! It's time to <em>execute</em> this upgrade! To save us some time, I'll paste some
JavaScript into the AJAX success function:</p>
