</p>
<p>This first display how much we will charge the user. And check this out: it could
be <em>positive</em>, meaning we'll charge them, or <em>negative</em> for a downgrade, meaning
they'll get an account credit that will automatically be used for future charges.</p>
<p>Finally, this shows the user <em>one</em> last alert to confirm the change. If they click
"Ok", the last callback will be executed. And it'll be our job to send one more AJAX
call back to the server to finally change their plan.</p>
<p>Let's do it!</p>

    
